### User Login
# @name user_login
POST {{host}}/login HTTP/1.1
content-type: {{json}}

{
    "email": "q@qq.com",
    "password": "123456"
}


### User Info
# @name user_info
GET {{host}}/user/q HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{user_login.response.body.$.token}}


### Users List
GET {{host}}/user/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{user_login.response.body.$.token}}


